@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Shipped
Shipped --> Reviewed : approve
Reviewed --> Draft : process
Draft --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Created : update
Archived : entry / log classroom
Created --> [*]
@enduml